@startuml
title Client Result Error Envelope (After)
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #111111
skinparam defaultFontColor #111111
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

actor "SDK Consumer" as Consumer #D6EAF8
component "createClient(...)" as Client #D5F5E3
component "Result Formatter\n(createResultFormatter)" as Formatter #F9E79F
component "normalizeAthenaError(...)\n(internal default path)" as Normalize #FDEBD0
component "AthenaResult<T>\n{ data, error: {\n  message, code, details, hint,\n  kind, table, operation, ...\n}, status, statusText,\nerrorDetails? }" as Result #E8DAEF
component "Hidden metadata\n__athenaNormalizedError" as Metadata #F5CBA7

Consumer --> Client : configure URL/key
Client --> Formatter : inject into from/rpc/query paths
Formatter --> Normalize : build normalized metadata automatically
Normalize --> Metadata : attach non-enumerable cache
Formatter --> Result : inline structured error envelope
Result --> Consumer : inspect error directly

note right of Result
`errorDetails` remains as a compatibility alias
for low-level gateway transport metadata.
end note

note bottom of Formatter
`experimental.enableErrorNormalization`
is retained only as a deprecated no-op.
end note
@enduml
